.TH TMPLR_MACROS 3 "__DATE__" "__VERSION__" "tmplr macros"
.SH NAME
tmplr_macros \- Template processing supporting macros
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B #include <tmplr/macros.h>
.PP
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B tmplr
provides several macros for convenient usage of the template processing functionality.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR tmplr (3)
